		{"id":"e_life_eff","fromNode":"node_lifestyle_first","fromSide":"left","toNode":"node_efficiency_rev","toSide":"right","label":"效率革命是實現生活方式優先的技術手段，透過極大化單位時間產出，換取自由時間。"},
		{"id":"e_eff_flow","fromNode":"node_efficiency_rev","fromSide":"bottom","toNode":"node_flow_profit","toSide":"top","label":"心流的高品質產出是效率革命的最佳解，兩者共同壓縮獲利所需的時間成本。"},
		{"id":"e_flow_life","fromNode":"node_flow_profit","fromSide":"right","toNode":"node_lifestyle_first","toSide":"bottom","label":"本路徑證明了高價值的單人勞動可以支撐高品質的生活，是實現「生活優先」的經濟保證。"},
		{"id":"e_life_phi","fromNode":"node_lifestyle_first","fromSide":"right","toNode":"node_120_identity","toSide":"left","label":"本概念提供了經營主權人生的哲學基礎，確定了「人高於公司」的價值優先順序。"},
		{"id":"e_eff_sys","fromNode":"node_efficiency_rev","fromSide":"right","toNode":"node_170_neuro","toSide":"left","label":"直接調用專注力神經科學工具，確保在極短時間內完成核心價值轉化。"},
		{"id":"e_flow_sov","fromNode":"node_flow_profit","fromSide":"bottom","toNode":"node_prod_types","toSide":"top","label":"透過掌握心流技能獲得數位時代的稀缺性，進而強化對時間與資產的主權。"},
